{"tid":610912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"失蹤女子深水埗墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-03-30T11:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T12:05:10.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"957802b4a305d5ca3f21bf3617930b93c6e483ed","tid":610912,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T11:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180330/large/1522402601_a504.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180330%2Flarge%2F1522402601_a504.jpg&h=a848bc5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員用帳篷蓋遺體，在場調查案件。(溫文學攝)<br />\n【18：50更新】警員調查後確定死者為一名女子，早前報稱失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n下午近5時，一名女子倒卧在深水埗柏樹街9號後巷一大廈的簷篷位置，途人發現懷疑事主由高處墮樓，於是報警。救護員到場證實事主當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n事主其後被移往地面，警員用帳篷蓋遺體，調查後確定死者為一名女子，早前報稱失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180330/58014986\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180330%2F58014986&d=5uhCr9pl1eHD9o0NWXfhUfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=81ecdd88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180330%2F58014986&h=8a8b82a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180330/58014986</a>"},{"pid":"28aa6297f2de5452e2be71ac114b3d2699fc6430","tid":610912,"uid":14250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:05:10.000Z","msg":"老謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}